https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Assassins-Creed-Shadows8-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> Lofi Girl向<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/assassins-creed-shadows">刺客信条阴影</a></em>的史诗配乐重新构想 - 在下面查看。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/gaming-features/assassins-creed-shadows-soundtrack-the-flight-3847251">飞行如何制作“刺客信条阴影”令人惊叹的超大型配乐</a></strong></li></ul><p>由作曲家Duo The Flight创建的<em>刺客信条阴影</em>的猛mm象配乐汇集了传统的日本乐器，即前卫Garde Pop，Techno和Rock。自从上周启动游戏以来，“原始配乐”的59首曲目已可以流式传输。</p><p>现在，开发人员ubisoft宣布了与Lofi Girl的合作，并从<em>刺客信条阴影</em>配乐中发行了新的专辑“ forking for lo-fi重新想象曲目”。</p><p> Lofi Girl在社交媒体上<a href="https://x.com/lofigirl/status/1904945119381405864" target="_blank" rel="noopener">写道</a>：“该系列将刺客信条阴影的隐秘魅力与舒缓的Lo-fi Beats融合在一起。” “加入纳伊（Naoe）在附近嬉戏的塔努基（Tanuki）嬉戏时，稍作宁静与宁静。增强您的游戏体验，或者只是用新的隐身节拍放松身心就可以放松身心。”</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">我们很高兴宣布Lofi Girl和<a href="https://twitter.com/Ubisoft?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@ubisoft</a>之间的独特合作，从刺客信条阴影配乐中提供了Lo-Fi重新构想。该系列将刺客信条阴影的隐秘魅力与舒缓的lo-fi节拍融合在一起。</p><p>加入naoe以获得… <a href="https://t.co/N3ofSWnFbL">pic.twitter.com/n3ofswnfbl</a></p><p> - <a href="https://twitter.com/lofigirl/status/1904945119381405864?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2025年3月26日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p> 20轨专辑现在可以流播，而乙烯基版将于今年晚些时候发行。</p><p> “像Ezio家族这样熟悉的旋律已被重新构想为更柔和，更大气的曲目 - 非常适合放松，学习或寻找重点。无论您是长期粉丝还是第一次发现这些主题，这都是值得在您的书架上添加的集合，” <a href="https://vinyl.lofirecords.com/products/lofi-girl-s-x-assassin-s-creed-shadows-various-artists" target="_blank" rel="noopener">列表</a>中写道。您可以<a href="https://vinyl.lofirecords.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处</a>预订乙烯基。 </p><p><iframe title="Spotify嵌入：Lofi Girl X Assassin＆Apos的信条阴影 - 隐形节拍放松身心" style="border-radius: 12px" width="100%" height="352" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen allow="autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; fullscreen; picture-in-picture" loading="lazy" src="https://open.spotify.com/embed/album/4VoRbaeHOWTIa3WYaGhr55?si=3HAEHi3JRNmPqKBiYAKHDA&#038;utm_source=oembed"></iframe></p><p> Speaking to <em>NME</em> about the score, <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/gaming-features/assassins-creed-shadows-soundtrack-the-flight-3847251">The Flight&#39;s Joe Henson said</a> : “At its heart, <em>Assassin&#39;s Creed</em> is a science fiction franchise and we always wanted to make a modern sounding score. When we did <em>Odyssey</em> , we intentionally made the music sound older but for this one, we wanted to combine traditional Japanese instruments with something more contemporary,” so they looked at Western films and turned to acts like <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/wu-tang-clan">Wu-Tang Clan</a> for inspiration.</p><p>同时， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/elon-musk-assassins-creed-shadows-gamergate-woke-3849423"><em>刺客的信条</em>X帐户在对埃隆·马斯克（Elon Musk）的批评后发出了辛辣的回应</a>。</p><p>在其他新闻中， <em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/grand-theft-auto-vi">Grand Theft Auto 6</a></em>粉丝坚信，期待已久的游戏将以<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/megan-thee-stallion">Megan Thee Stallion</a>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/grand-theft-auto-6-megan-thee-stallion-collab-radio-release-3849469">出现为特色</a>。</p><p>帖子<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/assassins-creed-shadows-epic-soundtrack-lo-fi-makeover-3849691">“刺客信条阴影”的史诗配乐已被</a>首次在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上出现。</p> ;
